As the quoted post's author, revoke permission for a quote of your post. Sends a revocation activity to the quoting instance. Only the `quotedPost`'s author may call this. Pass `actingAccountId` when the quoted post was authored by an organization account you belong to.
"""
input RevokeQuoteInput {
  """
  Optional `Account` ID that changes viewer-relative checks to an organization account managed by the authenticated viewer. Omit this argument to use the authenticated viewer's personal account.
  """
  actingAccountId: ID

